    {
        "content": "<p>Not an answer to the question about limits, but diagrams of this sort do come up in the theory of lax-idempotent 2-monads, where they in fact extend to the entire \"simplex 2-category\" (an enhancement of the simplex category to a 2-category making various face and degeneracy operators adjoint).</p>",
        "id": 193453281,
        "sender_full_name": "Mike Shulman",
        "timestamp": 1586440611
    }
